item.title: OpenSSL Video
item.description: New video I've wanted to make videos for a while now, and I finally have. I rehearsed for a couple iterations now, I wrote the outline and all the commands out before hand; [[public:linux:common#openssl|here is where you can view the outline/commands]] . Everything went pretty smoothly, everybody I spoke to in my circle spoke positively about it, I wish I could get a couple more reactions about the technical content. I tried to upload the video to a public locations: vimeo <https://vimeo.
